<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Server Patching Notification</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            color: #333333;
        }
        .container {
            width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        h2 {
            color: #2a7ae2;
        }
        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        th, td {
            padding: 10px;
            border: 1px solid #dddddd;
            text-align: left;
        }
        th {
            background-color: #f2f2f2;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            color: #777777;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Upcoming Server Patching Notification</h2>
        <p>Hello,</p>
        <p>The following servers are scheduled for patching:</p>

        <table>
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th>Server Name</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                {% for host in ansible_play_hosts_all | sort %}
                <tr>
                    <td>{{ host }}</td>
                </tr>
                {% endfor %}
            </tbody>
        </table>

        <p>Please ensure that any critical services are prepared.</p>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>This is an automated message sent by Ansible.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
